Update Notes
=============

- Fixed an issue where the landscape editor was
not available for some people
- Fixed an issue where there would be no retreat
time for Mine and Dynamite on custom scheme
with 3 or 5 seconds set
- You can now scroll the list of available lobbies
when searching for a player match.
- You can now skip past the intro movies
and title screen with a gamepad.
- Fixed a crash when entering a story level
after playing a multiplayer match with a
smaller loadout of classes.
- Custom schemes now appear as such in WormNet.
- Fixed an issue where cancelling joining a channel
in WormNet would cause a softlock
- Fixed an issue where cancelling leaving a
WormNet scheme would cause a softlock.
- You can now add Skip Go and Surrender to a scheme
- You can now cancel searching for a game.
- Fixed an issue where narration was not
muted when all other sounds were
